{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534/pid-max-and-min-command-fails-to-limit"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1534/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "title": "PID max and min command fails to limit when set to 0 (zero)", "component": {"name": "common::PID", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/294152.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 2, "content": {"raw": "[This logic here](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/8332b61f8485008d7c2887ebd412bc097f62181a/gazebo/common/PID.cc?at=default#cl-151) precludes max or min command limits to be zero.\r\nI.e. if either `cmdMax` or `cmdMin` is 0, the controller does not limit the effort at all.\r\n\r\nWe should remove the check against zeros:\r\n~~~\r\n  if (this->cmd > this->cmdMax)\r\n    this->cmd = this->cmdMax;\r\n  if (this->cmd < this->cmdMin)\r\n    this->cmd = this->cmdMin;\r\n~~~", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p><a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/8332b61f8485008d7c2887ebd412bc097f62181a/gazebo/common/PID.cc?at=default#cl-151\" rel=\"nofollow\">This logic here</a> precludes max or min command limits to be zero.\nI.e. if either <code>cmdMax</code> or <code>cmdMin</code> is 0, the controller does not limit the effort at all.</p>\n<p>We should remove the check against zeros:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  if (this-&gt;cmd &gt; this-&gt;cmdMax)\n    this-&gt;cmd = this-&gt;cmdMax;\n  if (this-&gt;cmd &lt; this-&gt;cmdMin)\n    this-&gt;cmd = this-&gt;cmdMin;\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-03-24T18:02:40.204678+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:22:55.070102+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1534}